==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Considerably
<hw>Con*sid"er*a*bly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a manner or to a
degree not trifling or unimportant; greatly; much.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The breeds . . . differ <qex>considerably</qex> from each
other.</q> <rj><qau>Darwin.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Considerance</ent>⟦br⟧
